---
layout: base.njk
title: "我的知识库"
description: "一个整理、推演、记录与实验的长期空间。"
pageClass: "page page--home"
permalink: index.html
---
<div class="page page--home">
  <section class="hero-band">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="home-hero">
        <div class="home-hero__content">
          <p class="eyebrow">Knowledge Garden</p>
          <h1>我的知识库</h1>
          <p class="home-hero__lead">一个整理、推演、记录与实验的长期空间，让笔记不只被保存，也能再次进入思考。</p>
          <div class="home-hero__meta">
            <span>{{ collections.notes | length }} 篇笔记</span>
            <span>静态发布</span>
            <span>支持全文搜索</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="home-hero__aside">
          <p class="home-hero__aside-label">站点说明</p>
          <p>这里主要整理数学、物理、计算机科学相关笔记，也保留一些实验性工具页面，用来验证“笔记 + 工具”能否形成一个更完整的学习界面。</p>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/notes/">浏览全部笔记</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="portal-panel portal-panel--controls">
        <div class="portal-search">
          <label class="portal-label" for="search-input">搜索笔记</label>
          <div class="portal-search__field">
            <input id="search-input" type="search" placeholder="输入关键词，按标题、标签或正文检索" aria-label="搜索笔记">
            <button id="search-clear" class="search-clear" type="button" hidden>重置</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="portal-filter">
          <label class="portal-label" for="tag-filter">主题筛选</label>
          <select id="tag-filter" aria-label="按标签筛选">
            <option value="">查看全部主题</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <p id="search-status" class="portal-status">当前展示最近更新的 10 篇笔记。输入关键词或选择主题后，将切换到独立结果区。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section" id="search-panel" hidden>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Search</p>
          <h2>搜索结果</h2>
        </div>
        <p id="search-summary" class="section-heading__meta">这里会显示关键词或标签对应的笔记结果。</p>
      </div>

      <div id="search-results" class="notes-grid notes-grid--search" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section" id="recent-panel">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Recent Notes</p>
          <h2>最近笔记</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-heading__meta">保留首页的“近期入口”角色，只展示最近更新的 10 篇内容。</p>
      </div>

      <ul id="notes-container" class="notes-grid notes-grid--recent">
        {% for note in collections.notes | reverse %}
          {% if loop.index0 < 10 %}
            {% set tag_text = note.data.tags | join(',') if note.data.tags else '' %}
            <li class="note-card" data-tags="{{ tag_text }}">
              <article class="note-card__body">
                <p class="note-card__eyebrow">最近更新</p>
                <h3 class="note-card__title">
                  <a href="{{ note.url }}">{{ note.data.title }}</a>
                </h3>
                <p class="note-card__meta">
                  <span>{{ note.data.date }}</span>
                  {% if note.data.tags and note.data.tags | length %}
                  <span>·</span>
                  <span>{{ note.data.tags | join(' · ') }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                </p>
                <p class="note-card__excerpt">{{ note.templateContent | excerpt(164) }}</p>
                {% if note.data.tags and note.data.tags | length %}
                <div class="note-card__tags">
                  {% for tag in note.data.tags %}
                  <span class="tag-pill">{{ tag }}</span>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
              </article>
            </li>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section page-section--secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Explore</p>
          <h2>探索入口</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-heading__meta">把“浏览全部内容”和“进入实验工具”并列展示，首页信息架构会更清晰。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <p class="feature-card__eyebrow">Archive</p>
          <h3>查看完整笔记目录</h3>
          <p>按时间倒序浏览所有条目，适合系统性回顾和查找旧内容。</p>
          <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="/notes/">进入所有笔记</a>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card feature-card--accent">
          <p class="feature-card__eyebrow">Lab</p>
          <h3>进入 Integral Lab V1</h3>
          <p>一个规则驱动的积分实验页面，用工具化交互验证数学操作流程。</p>
          <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/tools/integral-lab/">打开实验工具</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<script src="/js/search.js" defer></script>
